213
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,400
Charge!

214
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,080
Jianming!

215
00:11:15,125 --> 00:11:16,320
Fang Jianming?

216
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,150
