217
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,119
Lord Qinghai...

218
00:11:22,850 --> 00:11:23,880
Your Highness!

219
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:25,719
- Tilan is in the carriage.
- Your Highness!

220
00:11:25,719 --> 00:11:26,679
